DocAttribute.Name: PredefinedType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Defines the type of the structural analysis model.

DocAttribute.Name: OrientationOf2DPlane
DocAttribute.Documentation: If the selected model type (PredefinedType) describes a 2D system the orientation is needed to define the upright direction to the focused plane (z-axes). This is needed because all data for the structural analysis model (structural members, structural activities) are defined by using 3-D space. The orientation is given in relation to the coordinate system of the project. By 3D systems this value is not asserted.

DocAttribute.Name: LoadedBy
DocAttribute.Documentation: References to all load groups to be analyzed.

DocAttribute.Name: HasResults
DocAttribute.Documentation: References to all result groups available for this structural analysis model.
